snippet.title: Chewy: Esc from F5 - Game Trailer (1995)
snippet.description:
Esc from F5 feat. Chewy  , official trailer.
Developed by New Generation Software
Published in 1995 by Blue Byte for PC (DOS), in Germany, in german language only.
An English language version was released in 1997 by Play Byte (for DOS and Windows).

Year : 1995.

Titles :
Ingame Title : Esc from F5 feat. Chewy
Original German Title : Chewy- Esc von F5

Trailer found on coverdisc of the French Magazine PC Team (Issue 4, July 1995)
